@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam defaultFontName WenQuanYi Micro Hei
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam maxmessagesize 140
skinparam ParticipantPadding 30
skinparam BoxPadding 8

title 企业RAG — 用户问答流程（ReAct Agent）

actor 用户 as User
participant "Vue 3 前端\n(WebSocket)" as Browser
participant "ChatHandler\n(ReAct 编排)" as Chat
participant "LlmProviderRouter\n(LLM 模型路由)" as LlmRouter
participant "AgentToolRegistry\n(工具注册中心)" as AgentTool
participant "HybridSearchService\n(两阶段混合检索)" as Search
participant "EmbeddingClient\n(查询向量化)" as Embedding
participant "UsageQuotaService\n(Token 配额)" as Quota
participant "ConversationService\n(会话管理)" as ConvSvc
database "Elasticsearch\n(向量+全文)" as ES
database "Redis\n(对话缓存 / 反馈)" as Redis
database "MySQL\n(对话 / 会话持久化)" as DB

== WebSocket 连接 ==

Browser -> Browser: 建立 WebSocket 连接\nwss://host/ws/chat/{jwtToken}
Chat -> Chat: jwtUtils.validateToken()\n提取 userId，注册 session
Chat -> Browser: {"type":"connection","sessionId":"..."}
Browser -> Browser: 心跳: __chat_ping__ 每 20s\n自动重连: 延迟 1.5s

== 发起问答（前置检查）==

User -> Browser: 输入问题
Browser -> Browser: 创建 user 消息 + 空 assistant 消息\n(状态: pending)
Browser -> Chat: WebSocket 发送问题文本
Chat -> Chat: rateLimitService\n.checkChatByUser(userId)
note right: Redis 滑动窗口\n超出限制返回 429

Chat -> ConvSvc: getOrCreateSession\n(userId, conversationId)
ConvSvc -> DB: INSERT / SELECT\nconversation_sessions\n(状态: ACTIVE)
ConvSvc --> Chat: conversationId (含 title)

Chat -> Redis: GET conversation:{id}\n(最近 20 条历史, TTL 7天)
Redis --> Chat: 最近 N 条消息 (JSON)
Chat -> Chat: generationStateService\n.createGeneration(...)

Chat -> Browser: {"type":"start","generationId":"...","conversationId":"...","timestamp":...}
Browser -> Browser: 更新 assistant 消息\n(status: loading)

== ReAct 推理循环（最多 4 轮 / 8 次工具调用）==

Chat -> Quota: reserveLlmUsage\n(userId, promptTokens, maxTokens)
Quota --> Chat: TokenReservationBundle

Chat -> LlmRouter: buildReActMessages\n(用户消息 + 历史 + 工具定义\n+ 反馈指导 + 知识库优先规则)
LlmRouter -> LlmRouter: 从 model_provider_configs\n读取 active LLM provider\n(DeepSeek / Qwen / ZhipuAI)

LlmRouter -> LlmRouter: POST /chat/completions\n(streaming, tool_choice=auto)
note right: OpenAI 兼容协议\ntemperature=0.3\nmax_tokens=2000

alt LLM 决定调用工具
    LlmRouter --> Chat: ReActTurn:\ntoolCalls=[{id, name, arguments}]
    Chat -> Browser: {"type":"tool_call","tool":"search_knowledge",\n"toolCallId":"...","status":"executing"}

    Chat -> AgentTool: executeTool(name, arguments, userId)
    AgentTool --> Chat: ToolExecutionResult\n(content + data)
    Chat -> Browser: {"type":"tool_call","tool":"...",\n"status":"success"|"failed"}

    Chat -> LlmRouter: 追加 assistant(tool_calls)\n+ tool 消息, 继续推理
    note right: 最多循环 4 轮\n最多 8 次工具调用\n超时 120 秒
else LLM 输出文本
    LlmRouter --> Chat: 流式 SSE chunks\n(逐 token 回调)
    Chat -> Browser: {"type":"chunk","chunk":"...",\n"generationId":"..."}
    Browser --> User: 打字机效果逐字显示
end

Chat -> Quota: settleReservation\n(reservationId, actualTokens)

== 工具: search_knowledge（知识库检索）==

Chat -> AgentTool: executeTool\n("search_knowledge", {query, topK=5})
AgentTool -> Search: searchWithPermission\n(query, userId, topK)

Search -> Embedding: embed([query], userId)\n(UsageType.QUERY)
Embedding --> Search: Float[2048] queryVector

alt 向量生成成功
    Search -> ES: KNN (k=topK×30, cosine, 权限过滤)\n+ keyword must-match (textContent)
    Search -> ES: BM25 rescore\n(window=recallK, queryWeight=0.2,\nrescoreQueryWeight=1.0, AND)
else 向量生成失败
    Search -> ES: 纯 BM25 文本检索 (minScore=0.3)
end

ES --> Search: Top-K 结果\n(fileMd5, chunkId, score,\ntextContent, pageNumber)

Search -> Search: 附加文件名 (从 MySQL file_upload)
Search --> AgentTool: List<SearchResult>
AgentTool -> AgentTool: 格式化: [1]..[N] 编号引用
AgentTool --> Chat: ToolExecutionResult\n(编号上下文 + metadata)

Chat -> Chat: buildReferenceMappings\n(ref# → {fileMd5, fileName,\npageNumber, retrievalMode, score})

note over AgentTool, ES
  <b>4 个 Agent Tools:</b>
  · search_knowledge — 混合检索知识库
  · generate_summary — 检索+LLM 摘要(流式)
  · submit_feedback — 存储评分到 Redis Hash
  · knowledge_stats — ES 统计 + MySQL 文档数
end note

== 流式生成与持久化 ==

Chat -> Browser: 持续推送 {"type":"chunk","chunk":"..."}

Chat -> DB: INSERT INTO conversations\n(userId, question, answer,\nconversationId, referenceMappingsJson)
DB --> Chat: 持久化成功

Chat -> Redis: SET conversation:{id} = 历史 JSON\nEXPIRE 604800 (7天)

Chat -> Browser: {"type":"completion","status":"finished",\n"referenceMappings":{"1":{fileMd5, fileName,\npageNumber, retrievalMode, score,...}}}

Browser -> Browser: 解析 markdown 引用模式\n"来源#N: 文件名 | 第X页"
Browser --> User: 显示完整回答\n可点击引用来源 → 新标签页预览

== 停止生成 ==

User -> Browser: 点击"停止"按钮
Browser -> Browser: GET /api/v1/chat/websocket-token\n(获取 cmdToken)
Browser -> Chat: {"type":"stop","generationId":"...",\n"_internal_cmd_token":"WSS_STOP_CMD_..."}
Chat -> Chat: cancelledGenerations\n.add(generationId)
Chat -> LlmRouter: StreamHandle.cancel()\n(取消上游 SSE 订阅)
Chat -> Browser: {"type":"stop","generationId":"...",\n"message":"响应已停止"}
Chat -> Quota: settleReservation\n(部分用量结算)

@enduml
